Eskom Says 321 Renewable Energy Companies Bid to Supply Electricity Grid

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-09-14T07:43:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-14/eskom-says-321-renewable-energy-companies-bid-to-supply-electricity-grid.html
Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd.,  South
Africa ’s state power utility, received more than 321
applications from renewable-energy project developers wanting to
connect to the company’s grid, Kannan Lakmeeharan, managing
director of operations and planning, said in a speech in
Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
